{"tid":1973581,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[GTA Online] [PC]R*化身Thanos大清洗玩家物業及載具","createTime":"2020-04-15T09:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T18:26:48.000Z","uid":74661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49fea7ef7b785a8a1de678677540750b0d541e25","tid":1973581,"uid":74661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:19:38.000Z","msg":"今日12點出完夜總會同地堡貨就OFF GAME食晏，食完晏返到屋企再入GAME就發現所有物業同載具都無晒，LEVEL同錢都無改變。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為自己中BUG再LOG-IN多幾次都係一樣無晒。即時問下GOOGLE大神，發現REDDIT都有大量苦主，應該係R*自己出咗事。<br />\n我已經去R* Support出咗ticket等佢搞，有冇巴打有同樣情況？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n初步發現：角色無啦啦多咗化妝（唔同人可能有唔同化妝），我就無啦啦搽咗紅唇膏。<br />\nR* Support就話我張ticket已經記錄咗同CLOSED，可能會集體搞。"},{"pid":"56d481fb6a052730e9e29a9e4f03d2cb928c2dc2","tid":1973581,"uid":43824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"same here"},{"pid":"11bddc801ef131d2cb86bc8c81e0f6cdd87934b1","tid":1973581,"uid":316590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"}]}